dct_title_s: Map of Greece : Athens - Thessaloniki / Hellēnikos Organismos Tourismou ; Dēmētrios Tsopelas ; Michalēs Katzourakēs. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Map is number 13, January 1969. Recto includes distance chart in kilometers showing routes with the use of ferry-boats. Verso: Ancillary map showing Athens in relation to major European cities. Ancillary "Map of communications in Greece," showing railways, domestic air routes, and domestic shipping routes.
